{"tid":1503400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場抗爭雙方都陷入左一個死局","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:09:46.000Z","uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db58b86d55f1ef809e026dd8e9edde03cd532bd3","tid":1503400,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"和理非 -&gt; 又會有人出黎斬人<br />\n勇武迫住行出黎 -&gt; 又會有人爆眼<br />\n之後又去玩機場 -&gt; 政府又會跪低<br />\n但一返返去和理非, 又有機會有人比人斬<br />\n點樣可以中止上面呢個loop  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />基本上做乜都係死<br />\n<br />\n講到尾, 好地地做乜整個送中條例, 我諗去到呢一刻潘生潘太有無所謂公道已經唔可以凌架係社會秩序之上 (當佢地唔好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 或者直接消滅陳同佳之後撤回草案完左佢啦好嗎"},{"pid":"91c03bf38363c533bca539c707131be8f5d2c951","tid":1503400,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5985ede8670615063ecfdc20d9d1e20f10bd4194","tid":1503400,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"直到美國拖冧支那"},{"pid":"783bd9133c05f746bbf6bd8583a077a595ee668e","tid":1503400,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22cc8b08227db2965a6a36ec4801fffff352bea4","tid":1503400,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"【新策略】狗仔隊採訪，令和理非都有勇武嘅效果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n破死局嘅方法就係用對警察嘅硬度對高官（合法），從而施加心理壓力令佢地付出代價。"},{"pid":"583fd49d080769bdd8eb3fdc3f8e7b314f1f4d03","tid":1503400,